Description copied from interface: IAFServer
Browses the media server for all child entries under the specified container object

Specified by:
browseChildren in interface IAFServer
Parameters:
objectId - Id of the container object to browse. Use IAFServer.ROOT_DIRECTORY to browse the server root directory
startIndex - 0 based index of the first entry under the container to browse
fetchCount - The max number of entries to browse for. Use IAFServer.FETCH_ALL to fetch all entries under the container
userData - Optional - userData that will be passed to callback
callback - A callback function to be invoked with the browse result
